  "prompt": "Can people see if you have viewed their instagram?",
  "response": "On Instagram, users cannot see who has viewed their profile or who has viewed their photos or videos in the feed. However, if you view someone's story or reel, they will be able to see that you have viewed it. Additionally, if you engage with their posts by liking or commenting, they will also see your interaction. For IGTV videos, the creator can see who has watched their content.",
